---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';


import ProjectDetails from '../../../components/ProjectDetails.astro';
import QBCancellationsSelected from './qb-cancellations-selected.jpg';
import QBbbSubWLog from './qb-breadboard-subs-w-log.jpg';
import QBbbSubWBucket from './qb-breadboard-subs-w-bucket.jpg';
import QBbbSubWCancel from './qb-breadboard-subs-cancellations.jpg';
import QBbbSubCanCust from './qb-breadboard-subs-cancellations-customers.jpg';
import QBFatMBuck from './qb-fatmarker-bucket.jpg';
import QBFatMSel from './qb-fatmarker-selection-to-bucket.jpg';
import QBBucket from './qb-bucket-prototype.jpg';
import QBInvoice from './qb-invoice.png';
import QBProjects from './qb-projects.png';
import QBUsers from './qb-users.png';
// import QBProvUsr from './qb-provision-users-sample.jpg';
import QBwireframe from './qb-wireframe.jpg';
import QBProvFrn from './qb-provisioning-frontpage.png';

---

<div id="quotingbill" class="section-space">
  <h3 class="section-header">
    <span class="bg-black text-yellow">QuotingBill</span> is a platform that makes
    recurring billing, accurately simple for tel-com.
  </h3>
  <ProjectDetails
    role="Principal designer + Front-end html/css/vue"
    projectDate="2019‚Äì2021"
    projName="QuotingBill.com"
    projUrl="https://quotingbill.com"
  />

  <div class="mx-auto">
    <div class="mx-auto my-16 text-gray-900 image-solid-high">
      <Image
        class={'pic-withloader'}
        src={QBCancellationsSelected}  
        sizes="(max-width: 1980px) 100vw, 1980px"
        alt="Customers page showing different products selected for cancellation"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-20 mt-8 sm:flex-row">

    <div class="flex-col max-w-sm space-y-4 text-base text-white">
      <p>
        In the last part of 2019, I worked on the design of QuotingBill to bring a
        simple and streamlined way to invoice the Telecommunications space to the
        market.
      </p><p>
        We deeply researched what the current market had to offer for billing and
        invoicing and started building a simple yet powerful experience for our
        customers from the ground up.
      </p>
  
      <p>
        From that research, we developed an internal process for building each
        section with intention and meaning for the global system and for each
        component.
      </p>
    </div>
    <figure class="max-w-6xl">
      <Image
      class={'pic-withloader'}
      src={QBwireframe}  
      sizes="(max-width: 1980px) 100vw, 1980px"
      alt="QuotingBill User Flow"
    />
      <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">QuotingBill User Flow</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>


  <h3 class="section-subtitle">Breadboarding</h3>
  <div class="max-w-sm my-6 text-base text-white">
    <p>We wired the whole process of cancelling a product from the very concept, to each of the steps in detail in order to define each step as needed.</p>
  </div>
  <div
    class="grid-cols-1 section-spread sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 pswp-gallery" id="breadboarding-gallery">
        <a href={QBbbSubWCancel.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBbbSubWCancel.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBbbSubWCancel.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
        src={QBbbSubWCancel}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="First, the steps for cancelling a susbcription"
      />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">First, the steps for cancelling a susbcription</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
    <a href={QBbbSubWLog.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBbbSubWLog.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBbbSubWLog.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={QBbbSubWLog} 
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Requests and activity log shows up"
        />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">Requests and activity log shows up</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
    <a href={QBbbSubWBucket.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBbbSubWBucket.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBbbSubWBucket.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
        src={QBbbSubWBucket}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="Lastly, handling multiple products and confirmations"
      />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">Lastly, handling multiple products and confirmations</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>

  </div>
  <h3 class="section-subtitle">Fat markers</h3>
  <div
    class="grid-cols-1 section-spread sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 pswp-gallery" id="fatmarkers-gallery">

    <a href={QBFatMBuck.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBFatMBuck.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBFatMBuck.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <Image
        src={QBFatMBuck}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="Fat marker for the bucket"
      />
    </a>
    <a href={QBFatMSel.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBFatMSel.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBFatMSel.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <Image
        src={QBFatMSel}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="Fat marker for the bucket selection"
      />
    </a>
    <a href={QBBucket.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBBucket.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBBucket.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
        src={QBBucket}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="The first html/css/js prototype"
      />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">The first html/css/js prototype</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
  </div>
  <h3 class="section-subtitle">Sections in details</h3>
  <div class="section-spread sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 pswp-gallery" id="sectiondetails-gallery">
    
   <a href={QBInvoice.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBInvoice.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBInvoice.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={QBInvoice}
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Customers page showing different products selected for cancellation"
        />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">Invoice page</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
   <a href={QBProjects.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBProjects.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBProjects.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={QBProjects}
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Customers page showing different products selected for cancellation"
        />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">Project page</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
   <a href={QBUsers.src}
      data-pswp-width={QBUsers.width} 
      data-pswp-height={QBUsers.height} 
      target="_blank">
      <figure>
        <Image
          src={QBUsers}
          sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
          alt="Customers page showing different products selected for cancellation"
        />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-white">
          Adding users to a third-party service through QuotingBill
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="section-spread sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="max-w-sm mt-8 text-base text-white md:col-start-2">
      <p>
        The end product comprises a full suite of helpers connected to other
        services to make invoicing metered usage simple and trackable.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- <Image
        src={QBProvUsr}
        sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
        alt="Fat marker for the bucket"
      /> -->
    <Image
      class={'pic-withloader'}
      src={QBProvFrn}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"
      alt="Fat marker for the bucket selection"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="section-spread">
    <div class="flex max-w-sm gap-4 p-8 mt-8 text-sm bg-selva text-oldpink rounded-2xl">
      <div class="text-lg">üëÄüïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è</div>
      <div><h4 class="mb-4 text-base font-semibold">Check QuotingBill from the inside <a href="https://fedebozo.quotingbill.io/" class="font-bold" target="_blank">in this playground.</a>
      </h4>
      <p>User ‚Üí <span class="font-mono bg-slate-200 text-slate-700">user@quotingbill.com</span></p>
      <p>Pass ‚Üí <span class="font-mono bg-slate-200 text-slate-700">Try-quoting-b1ll-now!</span></p></div>      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
